Yeah, goodnight, now get otta here!

::Striker::

Striker laughs as he is pushed into the soot, grabbing Spears and pushing her 
in as well. His back was completely black, and would probably be hard to 
clean, but he didn't care, he was having fun.

"I don't give up that easilly!" he says, pushing her into the soot with one 
hand, and using the other to throw more on her.
